build/
cmake-build*/
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/install_manifest.txt
**/Makefile
**/*.ninja
**/*.ninja_deps
**/*.ninja_log
compile_commands.json

